data.description: ONE OF A KIND- PRIVACY-gated home on 2.1850 acres of peacefulness. This UNIQUE property boasts Main one level home with open concept large living room with stone wood fireplace, dining, kitchen with granite and LOVELY cabinets, laundry/mud room with utility sink, LARGE primary bedroom, fireplace &  door to back deck and hot tub, guest room, nice bathroom with walk in shower (handicapped) double vanities, office and front enclosed screened in porch ALL HAVE BEEN TOTALLY UPDATED! Then there is the GUEST HOME with Fully stocked kitchen, living room with fireplace, bedroom, bathroom with walk in shower, covered front porch. THEN there is the HAPPY PLACE> Timerland building with custom built ramp, complete build out with tung and groove ceiling and 1'' rainbow poplar on the walls, 100'' projector screen MOVIE THEATRE, BAR AREA, fireplace and plenty of space to entertain guests! Double garage and workshop with epoxy flooring, the landscaping is to die for with a creek running on the back of the property with outdoor kitchen, large-firepit and another outdoor stone fireplace, which is the perfect setting for a wedding or social event. This could be WONDERFUL WEDDING VENUE or AIRBNB,  there is also a RV PARKING area with 20 amp, 30 amp & 50 amp service, complete with wood shed and splitter. Home comes furnished- see attached list. ALSO> there is a PONTOON BOAT and 2020 RANGER- that could be available to the buyer!  possiblities are endless, this is a must see and all interested buyers must be qualified before showing the property. Schedule your showing today, Request from your agent the complete list of UPDATES and items to remain in the home. NEAR CHEROKEE NATIONAL PARK and LAUREL MARINA/ S HOLSTON LAKE..unbelieveable location for outdoor recreation and acitivities
